{"word":"G2433 - ἱλάσκομαι - hiláskomai - hil-as'-kom-ahee - Be merciful","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἱλάσκομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hiláskomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hil-as'-kom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be merciful</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கிருபையாயிரு, நிவர்த்திசெய்"},{"paragraph":"1. to render propitious to oneself, to appease, conciliate to oneself"},{"paragraph":"2. to expiate, make propitiation for"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from the same as <a href=\"#/G2436 - ἵλεως - híleōs - hil'-eh-oce/2436\">G2436</a>; to <i>conciliate</i>, that is, (transitively) to <i>atone</i> for (sin), or (intransitively) <i>be propitious:</i> - be merciful, make reconciliation for.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2433/2433\">G2433</a>, <a href=\"#/G2434/2434\">G2434</a>, <a href=\"#/G2435/2435\">G2435</a>, <a href=\"#/G2436/2436\">G2436</a>"}]}